        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your dive and water sports gear fresh and long-lasting with the GEAR AID Wetsuit Shampoo and BCD Cleaner Deluxe Kit. This two-piece kit is specially formulated to clean and condition neoprene wetsuits, drysuits, booties, and life jackets. The Revivex Wetsuit and Drysuit Shampoo gently removes salt, chlorine, and residue that can break down neoprene and cause unpleasant odors over time. Ideal for scuba divers, surfers, and swimmers, this cleaner helps extend the life of your equipment while leaving it clean and ready for your next adventure. Regular use keeps your BCD and neoprene gear soft, flexible, and free from buildup, ensuring reliable performance every time you hit the water.",
